OL,3,CModern slavery survivor 'broken' after
OL,4,Cbecoming trapped in life as a care
OL,5,Cworker
OL,7,FWarning: This article discusses topics
OL,8,Fincluding sexual exploitation, abuse
OL,9,Fand suicide.
OL,11,FA survivor of modern slavery said she
OL,12,F"wanted to end her life", after being
OL,13,Fforced to work night and day in a
OL,14,Fbread factory and as a care worker.
OL,16,FAt the age of 20, Rohima moved to the
OL,17,FUK from Bangladesh to study a masters
OL,18,Fin global marketing. But what should
OL,19,Fhave been an opportunity to change her
OL,20,Flife for the better instead brought
OL,21,Fher trauma and fear.
