OL,7,FModern slavery is a serious, and often
OL,8,Fhidden crime, where one person is
OL,9,Fexploited by another for personal or
OL,10,Ffinancial gain. It exists in many
OL,11,Fforms, from trafficking and forced
OL,12,Flabour, to domestic servitude and
OL,13,Fcriminal or sexual exploitation.
OL,15,FThe number of referrals of potential
OL,16,Fvictims of modern slavery made to the
OL,17,FHome Office, are at the record high in
OL,18,Fthe UK. According to the charity
OL,19,FUnseen, it's crime that has become
OL,20,Fentrenched into nearly every sector.
