OL,3,CModern slavery survivor 'broken' after
OL,4,Cbecoming trapped in life as a care
OL,5,Cworker
OL,7,FRohima, which is not her real name,
OL,8,Fhas told ITV News that she still
OL,9,Fsuffers with complex PTSD after her
OL,10,Fharrowing experience.
OL,12,FThere were no prosecutions on her
OL,13,Fcase, but it has left scars she is now
OL,14,Fdetermined to heal.
OL,16,FRohima, who is now 26, had a student
OL,17,Fvisa which meant she could work 20
OL,18,Fhours a week. With that in mind, she
OL,19,Fwas put in touch with what she though
OL,20,Fwas a legitimate agency.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/14
