OL,7,FShe said she then became under the
OL,8,Fcontrol of one man who first forced
OL,9,Fher to work in a bread factory.
OL,11,F"I didn't sleep, I was like a robot. I
OL,12,Fworked 50 hours (a week) but he (paid)
OL,13,Fme 20 hours.
OL,15,F"It was like all the night we had to
OL,16,Fstand up, and just one hour we have a
OL,17,Fbreak. That's it.
