OL,7,F"I was feeling so alone. When he
OL,8,Fcalled me, I had to pick up the call.
OL,9,FWhen he say me to come that place, I
OL,10,Fhad to go that place.
OL,12,F"When I'm going to work, they still
OL,13,Ffighting with me, talking to be badly.
OL,14,FAnd you know, bullying me, those
OL,15,Fthings. I was crying and I was
OL,16,Fmentally so broken."
