OL,7,FOne day, Rohima was sick but said she
OL,8,Fwas denied time off - instead she says
OL,9,Fshe was taken to a hotel by a man who
OL,10,Fdrugged and raped her, which he filmed
OL,11,Fto use as blackmail.
OL,13,FShe told ITV News that she was then
OL,14,Fforced to return to Bangladesh to
OL,15,Fmarry her perpetrator's cousin, so he
OL,16,Fcould get a visa to enter the UK.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/14
