OL,7,FOn her return, Rohima describes how
OL,8,Fshe was then forced into domiciliary
OL,9,Fcare work, visiting up to six elderly
OL,10,Fpatients a day, caring for their every
OL,11,Fneeds.
OL,13,FRohima said: "I didn't get paid that
OL,14,Fmuch. I'm working for (a) whole month,
OL,15,Fbut I'm getting #500, this was my
OL,16,Fhighest wage. I had to send the money
OL,17,F(to the) owner.
OL,19,F"Everything it was too much for me. I
OL,20,Fjust wanted to end my life."
