OL,7,FEventually, Rohima said the other
OL,8,Fworkers being exploited at the agency
OL,9,Fcontacted the police and an
OL,10,Finvestigation was launched.
OL,12,FRohima was initially afraid of the
OL,13,Fpolice and did not trust the charities
OL,14,Foffering her help.
OL,16,FBut she found the strength to accept
OL,17,Fthe help, and spent two years
OL,18,Frecovering at a Salvation Army safe
OL,19,Fhouse in the South West.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/14
