OL,7,FIt is one of the largest in the
OL,8,Fcountry, and cares for up to 32 female
OL,9,Fvictims of modern slavery, at any one
OL,10,Ftime.
OL,12,FThe safe house offers wraparound care,
OL,13,Fhealth and legal support, which is
OL,14,Fpart-funded by the government.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/14
