OL,7,FWhen asked about how the safe house
OL,8,Fbenefits the women, manager Gemma
OL,9,FKirby, said: "I think first and
OL,10,Fforemost, is how safe they feel here
OL,11,Fand that is really important to enable
OL,12,Fsomebody to start of the journey of
OL,13,Frecovery.
OL,15,F"We've helped a lot of women into work
OL,16,Fso they feel they're able to
OL,17,Fcontribute to society. We've also
OL,18,Fsupported women to take part in police
OL,19,Finvestigations, go to court to see
OL,20,Ftheir perpetrators brought to justice.
