OL,7,F"For me that's a real personal success
OL,8,Fthat it goes as far as that."
OL,10,FHow are potential modern slavery
OL,11,Fvictims identified?
OL,13,FWhen a potential victim of modern
OL,14,Fslavery is identified, often by a
OL,15,Ffirst responder like a police officer,
OL,16,Ftheir case has to be assessed under
OL,17,Fthe National Referral Mechanism (NRM).
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/14
